narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: As its name suggests, great and important for anyone who wants an introduction to macroeconomics. The workload is pretty manageable as well.
The seminar is a more engaging experience for a student, a more competitive curve, and a good chance to get to know one of the amazing economics teachers at the school. You get what you put in.
It's econ. Kind of dry so only take it if you have to
